criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  age between 18 and 38 years;

          -  diagnosis of breast cancer (BC)

          -  indication for neoadjuvant chemotherapy;

          -  body mass index (BMI) ≤27kg/m2; regular ovulatory cycles;

          -  transvaginal ultrasound showing the presence of two ovaries with an antral follicle
             count (AFC) between 10 and 30 follicles;

          -  affiliation to the national social security system.

          -  Written informed consent was obtained from all participants

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  - previous chemotherapy, ovarian surgery or endometrioma;
